<p>
In this example, the first statement does not add a newline, so the output appears on a single line:
</p>

<console>
<output>
Goodbye, cruel world
</output>
</console>

<p>
Notice that there is a space at the end of the first string, which appears in the output just before the word <c>cruel</c>.
</p>
